General.Name: Ornapaper Bhd
General.Description: Ornapaper Berhad, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture and sale of corrugated boards and carton boxes for the manufacturing sector in Malaysia, Asia, and the United States. The company provides corrugated boxes in various types, including regular slotted cartons, top and bottom, five panel folders, half and full overlap slotted cartons, L and H shape, nesting, corrugated pads, and die-cut corrugated boxes. It also supplies measuring cardboard boxes and corrugated flutes comprising single face, single wall, double wall, and triple wall corrugated sheetboards. In addition, it offers paper-based stationery products; and logistics and transportation services. The company serves electronics and electrical, food and beverages, furniture, textile and garments, rubber and plastic, hardware and steel, chemical products, sports, healthcare, stationery, and agriculture industries, as well as other stand-alone converters industry. Ornapaper Berhad was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Malacca, Malaysia.
